---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout locale="nl" title="Meeting Ingepland — ClosersMatch" description="Je meeting met Stefan staat gepland. Dit zijn de vervolgstappen: het gesprek, het intakeformulier en starten met je closer." noindex={true}>

  <!-- ================================================
       HERO
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="ty-hero">
    <div class="container container--narrow ty-hero__inner">
      <div class="ty-hero__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
      </div>
      <span class="label label--red">Meeting ingepland</span>
      <h1 class="ty-hero__title">Je meeting met Stefan<br />staat gepland.</h1>
      <p class="ty-hero__body">
        Je ontvangt een bevestiging per e-mail met een link om de afspraak toe te voegen aan je agenda. Hieronder lees je precies wat er gebeurt tussen nu en het moment dat jouw eerste closer aan de slag gaat.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       VERVOLGSTAPPEN TIMELINE
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section ty-steps">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="ty-steps__header">
        <span class="label">De vervolgstappen</span>
        <h2 class="h2 ty-steps__title">Van deze meeting<br />naar je eerste gesloten deal.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="ty-steps__timeline">

        <div class="ty-step ty-step--done">
          <div class="ty-step__left">
            <div class="ty-step__circle ty-step__circle--done" aria-label="Afgerond">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ty-step__line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ty-step__body">
            <span class="ty-step__tag">Afgerond</span>
            <h3 class="ty-step__title">Meeting ingepland</h3>
            <p class="ty-step__text">Je hebt een tijdstip gekozen dat je uitkomt. Check je inbox voor de bevestiging en agenda-uitnodiging.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ty-step">
          <div class="ty-step__left">
            <div class="ty-step__circle">02</div>
            <div class="ty-step__line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ty-step__body">
            <h3 class="ty-step__title">Het gesprek met Stefan</h3>
            <p class="ty-step__text">Tijdens het gesprek bespreken we jouw behoeften, je product en de uitdagingen waar je tegenaan loopt. We bespreken wat je zoekt in een closer of appointment setter, en verkennen samen hoe ClosersMatch de juiste match voor jouw bedrijf kan maken.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ty-step">
          <div class="ty-step__left">
            <div class="ty-step__circle">03</div>
            <div class="ty-step__line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ty-step__body">
            <h3 class="ty-step__title">Het intakeformulier</h3>
            <p class="ty-step__text">Direct na het gesprek ontvang je ons intakeformulier. Het invullen kost een paar minuten en geeft ons alles wat we nodig hebben om de closer te vinden die past bij jouw branche, salesstijl en dealgrootte.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ty-step ty-step--last">
          <div class="ty-step__left">
            <div class="ty-step__circle ty-step__circle--last">04</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ty-step__body">
            <h3 class="ty-step__title">Starten met je closer</h3>
            <p class="ty-step__text">Zodra de intake compleet is, matchen we je binnen 48 uur met een CM Certified closer. De onboarding op jouw product en markt is gratis en inbegrepen. Daarna gaat je closer direct aan de slag — op no cure no pay.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       AFSLUITING
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="ty-closing">
    <div class="ty-closing__inner">
      <h2 class="ty-closing__title">Nog vragen in de tussentijd?</h2>
      <p class="ty-closing__body">
        Neem gerust contact op, we helpen je graag.<br />
        <a href="tel:+31634835912">+31 6 3483 5912</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="mailto:info@closersmatch.nl">info@closersmatch.nl</a>
      </p>
      <a href="/nl" class="ty-closing__back">← Terug naar de homepage</a>
      <p class="ty-closing__brand">ClosersMatch. <span>The Revenue Ecosystem.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ====================================================
     HERO
  ==================================================== */
  .ty-hero {
    padding: 140px 0 60px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ty-hero__inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ty-hero__icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-red);
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .ty-hero__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin: 16px 0 20px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .ty-hero__body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .ty-hero { padding: 110px 0 48px; }
  }

  /* ====================================================
     STEPS TIMELINE
  ==================================================== */
  .ty-steps { background: #F9FAFB; }

  .ty-steps__header {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ty-steps__title {
    margin-top: 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .ty-steps__timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ty-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ty-step__left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    width: 56px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ty-step__circle {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-red);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    z-index: 1;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ty-step__circle--done {
    background: var(--color-black);
  }

  .ty-step__circle--last {
    background: var(--color-black);
  }

  .ty-step__line {
    width: 2px;
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--color-gray-border);
    margin: 4px 0;
    min-height: 24px;
  }

  .ty-step__body {
    padding: 0 0 40px 24px;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  .ty-step--last .ty-step__body {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .ty-step__tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-red);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .ty-step__title {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .ty-step__text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  /* ====================================================
     AFSLUITING
  ==================================================== */
  .ty-closing {
    background: var(--color-black);
    padding: 100px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ty-closing__inner {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ty-closing__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ty-closing__body {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .ty-closing__body a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .ty-closing__body a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .ty-closing__back {
    display: inline-block;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .ty-closing__back:hover {
    border-color: #fff;
  }

  .ty-closing__brand {
    margin-top: 48px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .ty-closing__brand span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }
</style>
